
Database aanmaken:

cd /net/aistaff/kleiweg/opt/agensgraph/bin

./initdb -D /net/aistaff/kleiweg/var/agensgraph/db_cluster -U peter -W

# ./ag_ctl -D /net/aistaff/kleiweg/var/agensgraph/db_cluster start
ag_start

./createuser -d -e -p 19033 -U peter -W p209327

./createdb -e -O p209327 -U peter -W -p 19033

================================================================

Gastgebruiker met alleen leesrechten:

cd /net/aistaff/kleiweg/opt/agensgraph/bin
createuser -p 19033 -P -U peter guest

starten:

/net/aistaff/kleiweg/bin/agens-guest

================================================================

Invoer corpus, voorbeeld:

    . pw
    ./alpino2agens alpinotreebank.dact | agens -b -q

Uitvoer:

    pg_dump -p 9333 peter -n fiets

SELECT
    tablename,
    indexname,
    indexdef
FROM
    pg_indexes
WHERE
    schemaname = 'fiets'
ORDER BY
    tablename,
    indexname;
